summary: The Death Metal Rocking Retsuko Gets Figures From Kidrobot
title: The Death Metal Rocking Retsuko Gets Figures From Kidrobot
body:
The Death Metal Rocking Retsuko Gets Figures From Kidrobot

Everyone’s favorite death metal panda is set to return to Netflix this year with a second season. For fans of Aggretsuko who can’t wait for the show, the good folks at Kidrobot have an entire collection coming up revolving around the Japanese anime musical comedy. They will be dropping merchandise throughout the year just in time for Season Two and they just revealed the most recent additions.
